text: Lola, you want banana too? I am trying to figure out the balance of mom life and taking care of myself. I'm taking the kids on a walk, and I want to try to get in a workout. What can I do with 20 minutes and a stroller? We're going to sprinkle in a few easy moves to get that heart rate up and those muscles working, all while keeping it real and mom-friendly. I feel like it's just having a little coach in my pocket. It always gives me new ideas and things that I never thought of before.
